# The New Default Stack\n\nBatch still exists, but it is no longer central. **Flink for flow. Iceberg for truth. Trino for insight.**\n\n---\n\n## Closing\n\nETL was the right abstraction for its time. That time is over. Stream first. Schema later. Adapt continuously.`,\n    date: \"2025-12-05\",\n    readTime: \"3 min read\",\n    tags: [\"data-engineering\", \"flink\", \"iceberg\", \"streaming\", \"etl\"],\n    slug: \"stream-first-schema-later-flink-iceberg\"\n  },"
